      <div class=\"seo-concept-faq-list reveal\">
        <details class=\"seo-concept-faq-item\" open>
          <summary>How is GEO optimization different from standard SEO?</summary>
          <p>While standard SEO focuses on broad keyword rankings, GEO optimization targets specific geographic areas. It involves Google Business Profile management, local citation building, and location-specific landing pages to capture \"near me\" and city-specific search intent.</p>
        </details>
        <details class=\"seo-concept-faq-item\">
          <summary>Can you handle businesses with multiple locations?</summary>
          <p>Yes. We specialize in multi-location brands and franchises, ensuring each branch has its own optimized presence while maintaining a cohesive national strategy.</p>
        </details>
        <details class=\"seo-concept-faq-item\">
          <summary>How long does it take to see local ranking improvements?</summary>
          <p>Local Pack and map rankings can often show movement within 4-8 weeks as profile optimizations and citation fixes are indexed. Organic city-page rankings typically build strength over 3-6 months.</p>
        </details>
        <details class=\"seo-concept-faq-item\">
          <summary>Do you create the location-specific content?</summary>
          <p>Yes. We research and write high-authority, hyper-local content for city pages, service area pages, and GBP posts that resonate with local audiences.</p>
        </details>
